11. Product layers

Layer 1: Personal

Use case: self-understanding and network hygiene

Questions answered:
	•	Who is changing my trajectory?
	•	Where am I drifting versus choosing?
	•	What interactions consistently stabilize or destabilize me?

This is the safest and likely highest-ROI starting point.

Layer 2: Team

Use case: org coordination and hidden structure

Questions answered:
	•	Who is actually central to coordination?
	•	Where are informal power centers?
	•	Which teams are resonant, brittle, or repulsive?

Layer 3: Ecosystem

Use case: founder, investor, community, market mapping

Questions answered:
	•	Which clusters are converging?
	•	Where are unstable alliance zones?
	•	Which actors have narrative mass but low coordination mass?

Do not start with Layer 3. Earn it.

