16. Visualization rules

This part must not get cheesy.

Render semantics
	•	position = reduced state-space coordinates
	•	trail = recent trajectory history
	•	mass halo = influence profile magnitude
	•	color family = cluster / alignment region
	•	line pulse = active interaction flow
	•	orbit thickness = confidence / stability, not aesthetic flair
	•	flicker / blur = uncertainty or volatility
	•	anchored rings = institutional constraints
	•	shockwave marker = major perturbation event

Do not make it look like a game first. Make it legible first.

